<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="In_other_media">In other media</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Mrs._Piggle-Wiggle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3" title="Edit section: In other media">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul>
<li>There is a musical entitled <i><a href="/wiki/The_Magic_Mrs._Piggle_Wiggle" title="The Magic Mrs. Piggle Wiggle">The Magic Mrs. Piggle Wiggle</a></i>.</li>
<li>In the 1990s, Mrs. Piggle-Wiggle was made into a TV series, starring <a href="/wiki/Jean_Stapleton" title="Jean Stapleton">Jean Stapleton</a>, of <i><a href="/wiki/All_in_the_Family" title="All in the Family">All in the Family</a></i> fame.</li>
</ul>
